to\": 500}, {\"ngram\": \"LOS ANGELES\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093Regan Smith\", \"from\": 501, \"to\": 526}, {\"ngram\": \"battle\", \"from\": 549, \"to\": 555}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 559, \"to\": 577}, {\"ngram\": \"a 100m backstroke duel\", \"from\": 596, \"to\": 618}, {\"ngram\": \"a historic result\", \"from\": 664, \"to\": 681}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Smith, 22, clocked 57.13 seconds to win the event at the US Olympic swimming trials last week, regaining the world record she first claimed as a 17-year-old in 2019 \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093 when she also set a 200m back world record.\", \"from\": 687, \"to\": 899, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 744, \"end\": 770, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2020_United_States_Olympic_trials_(swimming)\", \"score\": 0.5975359342914057, \"rank\": 0.6735395189005082, \"text\": \"US Olympic swimming trials\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2020_United_States_Olympic_trials_(swimming)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2020_United_States_Olympic_trials_(swimming)\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Smith\", \"from\": 687, \"to\": 692}, {\"ngram\": \"57.13 seconds\", \"from\": 706, \"to\": 719}, {\"ngram\": \"the event\", \"from\": 727, \"to\": 736}, {\"ngram\": \"the world record\", \"from\": 792, \"to\": 808}, {\"ngram\": \"a 200m back world record\", \"from\": 874, \"to\": 898}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A crisis of confidence and drop in form saw Smith settle for two silver medals and a bronze at the pandemic-delayed Tokyo Olympics, where fellow 22-year-old McKeown won the 100m and 200m backstroke.\", \"from\": 901, \"to\": 1099, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1017, \"end\": 1031, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.9840403915970677e-19, \"text\": \"Tokyo Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2020_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A crisis\", \"from\": 901, \"to\": 909}, {\"ngram\": \"confidence\", \"from\": 913, \"to\": 923}, {\"ngram\": \"drop\", \"from\": 928, \"to\": 932}, {\"ngram\": \"form\", \"from\": 936, \"to\": 940}, {\"ngram\": \"Smith\", \"from\": 945, \"to\": 950}, {\"ngram\": \"two silver medals\", \"from\": 962, \"to\": 979}, {\"ngram\": \"a bronze\", \"from\": 984, \"to\": 992}, {\"ngram\": \"fellow 22-year-old McKeown\", \"from\": 1039, \"to\": 1065}, {\"ngram\": \"the 100m\", \"from\": 1070, \"to\": 1078}, {\"ngram\": \"200m backstroke\", \"from\": 1083, \"to\": 1098}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Aussie, who first claimed the 100m back world record in 2021, lowered both the 100m and 200m marks in 2023 and clocked the second-fastest 200m backstroke time ever at the Australian trials in June.\", \"from\": 1101, \"to\": 1302, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1276, \"end\": 1286, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.9999679152610474, \"rank\": 3.077214885822289e-05, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Aussie\", \"from\": 1101, \"to\": 1111}, {\"ngram\": \"the 100m back world record\", \"from\": 1131, \"to\": 1157}, {\"ngram\": \"both the 100m\", \"from\": 1175, \"to\": 1188}, {\"ngram\": \"200m marks\", \"from\": 1193, \"to\": 1203}, {\"ngram\": \"the second-fastest 200m backstroke time\", \"from\": 1224, \"to\": 1263}, {\"ngram\": \"June\", \"from\": 1297, \"to\": 1301}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Smith, who has been re-energised by working with coach Bob Bowman, former mentor of Olympic superstar Michael Phelps, was thrilled to break out of her backstroke doldrums weeks before an expected meeting with the Australian star on the sport\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s biggest stage.\", \"from\": 1304, \"to\": 1564, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1359, \"end\": 1362, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bob_Bryan\", \"score\": 0.8218685855295298, \"rank\": 0.21673793623371407, \"text\": \"Bob\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bob_Bryan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bob_Bryan\"}, {\"begin\": 1363, \"end\": 1369, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bowman_Gum\", \"score\": 0.6227448611113158, \"rank\": 0.6057940478945644, \"text\": \"Bowman\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bowman_Gum\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bowman_Gum\"}, {\"begin\": 1406, \"end\": 1420, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Phelps\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1961340130219822e-60, \"text\": \"Michael Phelps\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Phelps\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Phelps\"}, {\"begin\": 1517, \"end\": 1532, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Australian_Star\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Australian star\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Australian_Star\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Australian_Star\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Smith\", \"from\": 1304, \"to\": 1309}, {\"ngram\": \"former mentor\", \"from\": 1371, \"to\": 1384}, {\"ngram\": \"her backstroke\", \"from\": 1451, \"to\": 1465}, {\"ngram\": \"an expected meeting\", \"from\": 1488, \"to\": 1507}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s biggest stage\", \"from\": 1536, \"to\": 1563}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI think 56 (seconds) is a possibility, for sure,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Smith said.\", \"from\": 1566, \"to\": 1632, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a possibility\", \"from\": 1593, \"to\": 1606}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Smith\", \"from\": 1617, \"to\": 1626}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cWhether it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s me or one of my competitors, who knows.\", \"from\": 1633, \"to\": 1690, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cWhether it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s me\", \"from\": 1633, \"to\": 1653}, {\"ngram\": \"my competitors\", \"from\": 1664, \"to\": 1678}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m not going to sell myself short, absolutely not.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Only five women have broken 58 seconds in the 100m back and all of them will be in Paris: Smith, McKeown, Aussie Mollie O\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099Callaghan, Canadian Kylie Masse and American Katharine Berkoff, who joined the club with her runner-up finish to Smith at the trials.\", \"from\": 1691, \"to\": 2010, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1836, \"end\": 1841, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999998212843, \"rank\": 1.7852430476932757e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1888, \"end\": 1896, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\", \"score\": 0.9999339355549827, \"rank\": 6.58857625292169e-05, \"text\": \"Canadian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\"}, {\"begin\": 1913, \"end\": 1921, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999895055293994, \"rank\": 1.0489654398672257e-05, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 1922, \"end\": 1939, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katharine_Berkoff\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Katharine Berkoff\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katharine_Berkoff\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katharine_Berkoff\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m\", \"from\": 1695, \"to\": 1700}, {\"ngram\": \"Only five women\", \"from\": 1752, \"to\": 1767}, {\"ngram\": \"58 seconds\", \"from\": 1780, \"to\": 1790}, {\"ngram\": \"the 100m\", \"from\": 1794, \"to\": 1802}, {\"ngram\": \"Smith\", \"from\": 1842, \"to\": 1847}, {\"ngram\": \"McKeown\", \"from\": 1849, \"to\": 1856}, {\"ngram\": \"Aussie Mollie O\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099Callaghan\", \"from\": 1858, \"to\": 1885}, {\"ngram\": \"the club\", \"from\": 1951, \"to\": 1959}, {\"ngram\": \"her runner-up finish\", \"from\": 1965, \"to\": 1985}, {\"ngram\": \"Smith\", \"from\": 1989, \"to\": 1994}, {\"ngram\": \"the trials\", \"from\": 1998, \"to\": 2008}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Even if O\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099Callaghan opts out of the backstroke to focus on other events, it promises to be a thriller, and Smith expects to be in the thick of it.\", \"from\": 2012, \"to\": 2160, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"O\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099Callaghan\", \"from\": 2020, \"to\": 2033}, {\"ngram\": \"the backstroke\", \"from\": 2046, \"to\": 2060}, {\"ngram\": \"other events\", \"from\": 2073, \"to\": 2085}, {\"ngram\": \"a thriller\", \"from\": 2105, \"to\": 2115}, {\"ngram\": \"Smith\", \"from\": 2121, \"to\": 2126}, {\"ngram\": \"the thick\", \"from\": 2144, \"to\": 2153}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cThat was an amazing race but it wasn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t a perfect race,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d she said of her record-setting trials final.\", \"from\": 2162, \"to\": 2269, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cThat\", \"from\": 2162, \"to\": 2169}, {\"ngram\": \"an amazing race\", \"from\": 2174, \"to\": 2189}, {\"ngram\": \"a perfect race\", \"from\": 2206, \"to\": 2220}, {\"ngram\": \"her record-setting trials\", \"from\": 2237, \"to\": 2262}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI know there\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s things that I can clean up and do better, and I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m going to work towards that.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Smith, who also won the 200m butterfly and 200m backstroke in Indianapolis to line up a trio of individual events in Paris, said the feeling of her world record swim was \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cso different\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d to her first, five years ago at the world championships.\", \"from\": 2270, \"to\": 2619, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2436, \"end\": 2448, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indianapolis\", \"score\": 0.9993482898472874, \"rank\": 0.0006453906856619998, \"text\": \"Indianapolis\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indianapolis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indianapolis\"}, {\"begin\": 2491, \"end\": 2496, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999998212843, \"rank\": 1.7852430476932757e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 2290, \"to\": 2296}, {\"ngram\": \"I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m\", \"from\": 2336, \"to\": 2341}, {\"ngram\": \"that.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Smith\", \"from\": 2364, \"to\": 2378}, {\"ngram\": \"the 200m butterfly\", \"from\": 2393, \"to\": 2411}, {\"ngram\": \"a trio\", \"from\": 2459, \"to\": 2465}, {\"ngram\": \"individual events\", \"from\": 2469, \"to\": 2486}, {\"ngram\": \"the feeling\", \"from\": 2502, \"to\": 2513}, {\"ngram\": \"her world record swim\", \"from\": 2517, \"to\": 2538}, {\"ngram\": \"different\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d\", \"from\": 2549, \"to\": 2561}, {\"ngram\": \"the world championships\", \"from\": 2594, \"to\": 2617}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cWhen you\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099re 17, when you\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099re a teenager and I had not really done much to my name yet \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093 it was very easy,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d she said.\", \"from\": 2621, \"to\": 2747, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my name\", \"from\": 2701, \"to\": 2708}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI had no pressure on me.\", \"from\": 2748, \"to\": 2775, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no pressure\", \"from\": 2757, \"to\": 2768}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nobody really expected much out of me, and so it was so easy to walk into races feeling so fearless and not really caring what the outcome was.\", \"from\": 2776, \"to\": 2919, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Nobody\", \"from\": 2776, \"to\": 2782}, {\"ngram\": \"races\", \"from\": 2850, \"to\": 2855}, {\"ngram\": \"the outcome\", \"from\": 2903, \"to\": 2914}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI really just shocked myself at that meet in 2019 because I didn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t believe I was capable of it.\", \"from\": 2921, \"to\": 3021, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that meet\", \"from\": 2956, \"to\": 2965}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now tonight, I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m in a much different place in my life.\", \"from\": 3022, \"to\": 3078, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Now tonight, I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m\", \"from\": 3022, \"to\": 3040}, {\"ngram\": \"a much different place\", \"from\": 3044, \"to\": 3066}, {\"ngram\": \"my life\", \"from\": 3070, \"to\": 3077}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m a lot older, obviously.\", \"from\": 3079, \"to\": 3108, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m\", \"from\": 3079, \"to\": 3084}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The pressure is a lot different.\", \"from\": 3109, \"to\": 3141, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The pressure\", \"from\": 3109, \"to\": 3121}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cBut I think I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099ve learnt a lot over these five years, and I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099ve had a lot of lows, in backstroke, in particular.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Smith said she felt it was a mental block that kept her from progressing in the backstroke.\", \"from\": 3143, \"to\": 3356, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"these five years\", \"from\": 3183, \"to\": 3199}, {\"ngram\": \"I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099ve\", \"from\": 3205, \"to\": 3211}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 3216, \"to\": 3221}, {\"ngram\": \"lows\", \"from\": 3225, \"to\": 3229}, {\"ngram\": \"backstroke\", \"from\": 3234, \"to\": 3244}, {\"ngram\": \"particular.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Smith\", \"from\": 3249, \"to\": 3269}, {\"ngram\": \"a mental block\", \"from\": 3291, \"to\": 3305}, {\"ngram\": \"the backstroke\", \"from\": 3340, \"to\": 3354}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cFor a long time, I viewed swimming as like a job, and it was a business trip.\", \"from\": 3358, \"to\": 3438, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a long time\", \"from\": 3365, \"to\": 3376}, {\"ngram\": \"swimming\", \"from\": 3387, \"to\": 3395}, {\"ngram\": \"a job\", \"from\": 3404, \"to\": 3409}, {\"ngram\": \"a business trip\", \"from\": 3422, \"to\": 3437}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I think there\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s a time and a place for that.\", \"from\": 3439, \"to\": 3485, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"there\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 3447, \"to\": 3456}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yes, I have a job to do, but at the same time this is just fun, and thank God it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s a sport.\", \"from\": 3486, \"to\": 3579, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a job\", \"from\": 3498, \"to\": 3503}, {\"ngram\": \"the same time\", \"from\": 3518, \"to\": 3531}, {\"ngram\": \"God it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 3560, \"to\": 3570}, {\"ngram\": \"a sport\", \"from\": 3571, \"to\": 3578}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This isn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t life or death.\", \"from\": 3580, \"to\": 3607, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This isn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t life\", \"from\": 3580, \"to\": 3597}, {\"ngram\": \"death\", \"from\": 3601, \"to\": 3606}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI just want to lean into the fun side 100 per cent and I think that just makes it a lot easier to go out there and let rip and give your best effort every single time.\", \"from\": 3609, \"to\": 3779, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the fun side\", \"from\": 3637, \"to\": 3649}, {\"ngram\": \"your best effort\", \"from\": 3744, \"to\": 3760}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And I know Kaylee will.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Meanwhile on June 22, Caeleb Dressel powered to victory in the 100m butterfly at the trials to line up another title defence in Paris, where Katie Ledecky will go for a historic fourth straight 800m freestyle gold.\", \"from\": 3780, \"to\": 4022, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3830, \"end\": 3844, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caeleb_Dressel\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Caeleb Dressel\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caeleb_Dressel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caeleb_Dressel\"}, {\"begin\": 3936, \"end\": 3941, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999998212843, \"rank\": 1.7852430476932757e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 3949, \"end\": 3962, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katie_Ledecky\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Katie Ledecky\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katie_Ledecky\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katie_Ledecky\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Kaylee will.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d\", \"from\": 3791, \"to\": 3806}, {\"ngram\": \"June\", \"from\": 3820, \"to\": 3824}, {\"ngram\": \"victory\", \"from\": 3855, \"to\": 3862},